{"hb48bf248gb78eg42begb1eeg0fa2b63d9f4a": ["((*who is it. what do they want. are we safe*))", "419b560c-143e-e6d2-ef04-48a516daf7d9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "2d571cb3-956b-9507-537e-f501ef98bc06"], "h997e9851gf78cg46bcgab21g134cd58bd3e8": ["Who are you? <i>What</i> are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "8cc845f0-06b4-afc4-b356-2a259a1db926"], "h10e57a79gca4eg42e6g9021gdd01b0253af5": ["((*closer. they're coming closer*))", "419b560c-143e-e6d2-ef04-48a516daf7d9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "d67a03e8-cfbb-caaf-9678-4fbc241a1107"], "hb603f804g2e3cg4d34g8a21g80ef752cb38b": ["<i>Probe your memories. What magic might this be?</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "2cddd4ed-1e5e-6ee3-8435-7b654ec67804"], "hf98228e7gd87fg48d4gad9fg49e7bf18606d": ["*Telepathic mushroom creatures - myconids - inhabit the Underdark. You must be nearing a myconid colony.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "41ae0bb2-f433-fb00-0472-bd7925c31193"], "h6139b5cegd390g4ae7gb5d5gc5b8b1af776f": ["*You cannot identify the voice's origins.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "59a01da8-d720-b369-03b3-75a922006dde"], "h849464bag3eafg4078g8926g22746bf214d8": ["<i>Consider the voice. What sort of creature speaks this way?</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "c2560fe2-ab3f-e256-ea7e-ff0096bdb4bf"], "h7a3b41e3g1a2cg4c81ga5eag308f637e4648": ["<i>This feels familiar. Search your memories...</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "126982ba-9705-7f0f-720c-47de6c0a8dd9"], "heff06bcfg9a70g46acg8f13g8394a2db5c3f": ["<i>Continue forward.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "8393a3ed-9fba-0c02-534b-734af16b804f"], "h025309d6gb512g461fgb1b3g5129b12d2ea9": ["((*more are coming*))", "419b560c-143e-e6d2-ef04-48a516daf7d9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "bbb9199a-93c8-4762-7241-a9322c85b660"], "h88aaeeb8g89f4g4065gbf96g44f5890aa6fe": ["*Your mind is a canyon, and the words echo from every crevasse.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "2b801b27-b1ce-92fc-633c-02174d9ef3c9"], "hdfecaae0ge349g427fga937gc8a17fcc5abe": ["((*they're coming. <i>they're coming</i>*))", "419b560c-143e-e6d2-ef04-48a516daf7d9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "e2e1c33a-6eda-5331-b3d0-45ccb5a643ed"], "h15e4b1b9g36a1g4249ga322g4ece992c1926": ["I don't know who you are, but you're not welcome in my head.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "67d6703a-0c18-f501-47dc-d8035bf479af"], "h315e1420g6bf4g4e4cg8381gdcf75545cc38": ["((*they're coming. <i>you're coming</i>*))", "419b560c-143e-e6d2-ef04-48a516daf7d9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "6fa757e7-339f-4f10-c95b-323555ad157a"], "hfff737f0g26c1g455cgb6d5g5015f1ca3fd7": ["<i>Still your mind. You have heard many voices - but never this one.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "f30b377b-a036-a88a-d280-672a317f8f3b"], "h8c53efb2geba4g43b1ga4ebgf75019937333": ["Who's coming? Cazador's minions? Have they found me?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "a4a722f3-0274-79e1-676c-2363621c9458"], "hc96575d7g6f50g4c6bgb978g480dcd806dd7": ["Come on, then. I'm not afraid of you!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "03a74650-f39c-3ee2-e268-82c136634dac"], "hd1922014g998eg4520ga385gc6e515eb288a": ["<i>You think of Shar - could she be speaking to you here at last, in the dark...?</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "0062d0ca-951c-a0a6-79e9-3277e6d8c9be"], "h21815f15gdd1bg4c6agb4cfgfd8811670679": ["<i>Ignore your tightening chest. Surely the devils hadn't found you down here?</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "f051999a-fd7b-fc04-f907-3cc3556da23e"], "h8242bb53g670cg4aa3g8d01g77a318f4f728": ["Enough of this mind-magic. Speak plainly!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "5c9387c5-154f-27dc-25d3-a9bf36fbe6a0"], "h46641fafg06c3g4b5fg86a1g04dee69595da": ["<i>Still your thoughts to this new voice intruding on you.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "acb1829e-556d-e412-0233-cbe0931883e5"], "h2a4cd317g9656g4473ga523gac334f749b3a": ["<i>Pray for fortitude against this mental trespass.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "38c2e24e-c92c-b7cf-3ade-1931c830d6f8"], "h835fa29cg7f0fg400cgb030g44a2c0b38622": ["<i>Ignore the voice.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_Alone.html", "f64c6348-aca6-7155-a8c9-d8e7c9669ec0"]}